00:32:44,950 --> 00:32:46,191
does a very good job of this, actually.

477
00:32:47,031 --> 00:32:51,014
The specific example I'll use of I'm driving the horse-drawn

478
00:32:51,655 --> 00:32:55,038
stagecoach, so I'm having to engage in precision and timing

