00:33:19,848 --> 00:33:24,351
a stealth action game, and in co-op it was a mandate on the level design side to try

486
00:33:24,391 --> 00:33:26,153
to support multiple styles of play.

487
00:33:26,570 --> 00:33:30,351
players being able to use action, being able to use stealth, being able to use gadgets

