00:34:26,017 --> 00:34:30,821
survive until the very, very end. But if you die, you're out for the round. You're going

500
00:34:30,841 --> 00:34:34,784
to be waiting for however long the round lasts until your friends are done and you get to

501
00:34:34,824 --> 00:34:41,870
listen to them laughing and screaming and yelling and enjoying themselves. What's interesting

502
00:34:41,890 --> 00:34:47,314
about this dynamic is that it makes survival itself a kind of victory. It just makes it

503
00:34:47,334 --> 00:34:49,756
kind of a slightly lower tier victory.

504
00:34:51,108 --> 00:34:54,448
At the end of the day, there can really only be one most valuable player.

