00:34:56,069 --> 00:35:02,390
And that pressure to say, well, I've survived the last few levels, I'd really like to be

506
00:35:02,430 --> 00:35:07,231
the hero, I'd like to be the MVP, means that players will, over time, tend to stick their

507
00:35:07,251 --> 00:35:07,551
neck out.

508
00:35:08,531 --> 00:35:10,892
They'll weigh the risks and the rewards and they'll give it a shot.

