00:35:36,417 --> 00:35:41,458
no man behind, this kind of concept works very well with this dynamic. And the recent

516
00:35:42,098 --> 00:35:45,939
Ghost Recon games, Grawl 1 and Grawl 2, did a very good job of leveraging this approach.

