00:36:02,246 --> 00:36:09,672
fit the fantasy of the two covert agents placed in harm's way, unable to be able to complete

521
00:36:09,692 --> 00:36:13,956
the mission unless both players are able to do it. So it fit, and it wouldn't necessarily

