00:37:32,666 --> 00:37:34,788
and to be immobilized on the ground bleeding to death,

539
00:37:35,808 --> 00:37:38,450
to have their teammate come rushing to their rescue,

540
00:37:39,410 --> 00:37:42,012
and to be within steps of reaching them

541
00:37:42,272 --> 00:37:45,093
and then get grabbed by another enemy in a chokehold.

