00:44:36,379 --> 00:44:38,280
that maybe you wouldn't have anticipated.

652
00:44:39,001 --> 00:44:41,742
So, after everything else I've said, at the same time,

653
00:44:42,303 --> 00:44:45,625
don't freak out, don't feel like you need to control the player experience

654
00:44:45,645 --> 00:44:47,686
for these two people or three people or four people.

655
00:44:48,807 --> 00:44:52,450
Their numbers will give them the added collective intelligence to tackle these problems.

